          "markText": "金融业的事业战略是，面对团块世代退休金这样的巨大资产，建立最强零售银行，所以想要增加从事零售业务的女性银行职员。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1748602910,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-05-30 19:01:50",
          "chapterUid": 23,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1675&rangeEnd=1731",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1675&rangeEnd=1731"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_18_1037-1102",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1037-1102",
      "markText": "她20岁回家参加成人仪式时，看到父亲无精打采、消瘦憔悴、脸色发黄，她才发现，以前大男子主义、顽固、横冲直撞的父亲现在已经非常虚弱。",
      "totalCount": 2014,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1037&rangeEnd=1102",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1037&rangeEnd=1102"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_33_391-462",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "391-462",
      "markText": "COMSN给员工们布置工作配额，制定不合理的排班表，以及出现不正当领取保费等情况，都是过度追求老龄化带来的商机，急于扩大业务而产生的负面影响。",
      "totalCount": 2010,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=391&rangeEnd=462",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=391&rangeEnd=462"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_20_1657-1715",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1657-1715",
      "markText": "另外，在从18岁工作到60岁的情况下，整个职业生涯的工资，正式员工是2亿500万日元，非正式员工只有5000万日元。",
      "totalCount": 2007,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1657&rangeEnd=1715",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1657&rangeEnd=1715"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_47_4901-4946",
      "chapterUid": 47,
      "range": "4901-4946",
      "markText": "本部位于富山市八尾町的园林业新村公司社长新村博明表示：“中学生们在这里，我们也不娇惯他们。",
      "totalCount": 2000,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=47&rangeStart=4901&rangeEnd=4946",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=47&rangeStart=4901&rangeEnd=4946"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_39_1442-1505",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "1442-1505",
      "markText": "政府根据经济财政运营基本方针，到2011年度每年削减2200亿日元的社会保障费，这种政策的恶劣影响就波及了医疗现场的工作人员。",
      "totalCount": 1980,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=1442&rangeEnd=1505",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=1442&rangeEnd=1505"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_12_657-714",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "657-714",
      "markText": "她的工作是策划、运营公司“导航”就业服务网站的内容，为其他公司策划入职介绍、手册，主页制作以及组织招聘活动的方法。",
      "totalCount": 1977,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=657&rangeEnd=714",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=657&rangeEnd=714"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_50_1854-1905",
      "chapterUid": 50,
      "range": "1854-1905",
      "markText": "有的年轻人，被农村地区的生活吸引，抛弃城市的终身雇佣这样的工作方式、生活方式，和地方上的居民一起生活。",
      "totalCount": 1956,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=50&rangeStart=1854&rangeEnd=1905",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=50&rangeStart=1854&rangeEnd=1905"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_23_1034-1081",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "1034-1081",
      "markText": "然而，即使女性好不容易成为正式员工，想要长期为公司工作、加倍努力，公司依然对她们“用后即弃”。",
      "totalCount": 1913,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1034&rangeEnd=1081",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=1034&rangeEnd=1081"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_54_2368-2453",
      "chapterUid": 54,
      "range": "2368-2453",
      "markText": "特别是，根据厚生劳动省省令和大臣告示，“如果不是六级中的四级以上残障，不宜入住支援中心”，所以让人担心的是，比起身体上的帮助，更需要看护、照顾的智力障碍者必须要离开设施。",
      "totalCount": 1909,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=54&rangeStart=2368&rangeEnd=2453",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=54&rangeStart=2368&rangeEnd=2453"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_31_800-885",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "800-885",
      "markText": "2000年4月，看护服务使用者有149万人，2005年增长了121%，达到329万人，看护保险财政从2000年的3兆6000亿日元增长到了2005年的5兆7000亿日元。",
      "totalCount": 1906,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=800&rangeEnd=885",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=800&rangeEnd=885"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_56_1002-1058",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "1002-1058",
      "markText": "访问宫城县的时候，笔者了解到，市、镇、村合并的弊害，不仅是对周边的居民产生了影响，也对在那里的公务员产生了影响。",
      "totalCount": 1906,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=1002&rangeEnd=1058",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=1002&rangeEnd=1058"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_56_2767-2814",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "2767-2814",
      "markText": "国家努力推进职业教育，学生从义务教育课程开始学习劳动法制的话，才更能够在成为社会人后发挥作用。",
      "totalCount": 1896,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=56&rangeStart=2767&rangeEnd=2814",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=56&rangeStart=2767&rangeEnd=2814"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_20_1842-1892",
      "chapterUid": 20,
      "range": "1842-1892",
      "markText": "纮子一边做着派遣员工的工作一边找工作，却很难找到和之前的工作工资水平相当的机会，更别说条件更好的了。",
      "totalCount": 1875,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1842&rangeEnd=1892",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=20&rangeStart=1842&rangeEnd=1892"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_22_3637-3666",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "3637-3666",
      "markText": "2005年5月中旬，生活在关西地区的父亲患癌症离开了人世。",
      "totalCount": 1845,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3637&rangeEnd=3666",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3637&rangeEnd=3666"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_22_672-710",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "672-710",
      "markText": "特别是大型制造商的承包商，交付日期严格，技术周期很快，所以工作环境更加恶劣。",
      "totalCount": 1842,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=710",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=672&rangeEnd=710"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_22_3134-3171",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "3134-3171",
      "markText": "正式员工一般可以期待工资根据工龄增长，然而非正式员工的增长曲线一直是平的。",
      "totalCount": 1837,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3134&rangeEnd=3171",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=3134&rangeEnd=3171"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_44_1947-2007",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "1947-2007",
      "markText": "对中国员工的管理、与中国政府的沟通、广告公关等对日本人来说比较难，日本企业要想在国际市场上不断成长，启用中国干部是关键。",
      "totalCount": 1761,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=1947&rangeEnd=2007",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=1947&rangeEnd=2007"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_10_2213-2254",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "2213-2254",
      "markText": "因为过于忙碌而无法约会，即使开始约会，也无法谈到关系很深的状态，没有办法一起相处。",
      "totalCount": 1747,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300101146&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2213&rangeEnd=2254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24d32130813ab8e02g0162a4?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=2213&rangeEnd=2254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300101146_56_792-836",
      "chapterUid": 56,
      "range": "792-836",
